  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5584577/" class="title-link">这是一本什么书？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5584577"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3601655/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3601655-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3601655/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大秋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-09-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-09-15 10:10:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5584577_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书游走于“历史分析与时事评论”与“游记随想”之间，定位很不明确。小小的一本书，想涵盖“历史、文化、政治”多个方面，势必什么东西都说不透、说不明白，不过《大中东行纪》这个标题似乎在说——这就是本普通的游记，你们不要读得太认真啊。 看了一下豆瓣评论，不少人读...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5584577/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">12有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
